'''Mainamoti Medical College''' is a private medical college in Baropara, [[Comilla]], [[Bangladesh]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/country/3-medical-colleges-fined-tk-1cr-1321324|title=3 medical colleges fined Tk 1cr|date=2016-11-27|newspaper=The Daily Star|access-date=2017-02-24|language=en}}</ref>
== History == The college was established on 21 February in 2011.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://mmmccomilla.com/about-us/|title=moinamoti medical college|date=2016-05-31|newspaper=Mainamoti Medical College|access-date=2017-02-24|language=en-US}}</ref> It was fined 10 million taka in November 2016 by [[Bangladesh High Court]] for admitting students that did not meet the admission requirements for medical college set by [[Ministry of Health and Family Welfare (Bangladesh)|health ministry]].<ref name=":0" />
