ium|M. felifacium]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma feliminutum|M. feliminutum]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma feriruminatoris|M. feriruminatoris]]<ref name=Mycoplasma>[http://www.bacterio.net/mycoplasma.html LPSN bacterio.net]</ref>'' *''[[Mycoplasma fermentans|M. fermentans]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma flocculare|M. flocculare]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma gallinaceum|M. gallinaceum]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma gallinarum|M. gallinarum]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma gallisepticum|M. gallisepticum]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma gallopavonis|M. gallopavonis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma gaetea|M. gaeteae]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma genitalium|M. genitalium]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma glycophilium|M. glycophilium]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma gypis|M. gypis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma haemocanis|M. haemocanis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma haemofelis|M. haemofelis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma haemomuris|M. haemomuris]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma haeosuis|M. haemosuis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma hominis|M. hominis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma hyopneumoniae|M. hyopneumoniae]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma hypopharyngis|M. hypopharyngis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma hyorhinis|M. hyorhinis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma hyosynovia|M. hyosynoviae]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma iguanae|M. iguanae]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma imatans|M. imitans]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma indiense|M. indiense]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma iners|M. iners]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma iowae|M. iowae]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma lacutcae|M. lacutcae]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma lagogenitalium|M. lagogenitalium]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma leachii|M. leachii]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma leonicptivi|M. leonicptivi]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma leopharyngis|M. leopharyngis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma lipofaciens|M. lipofaciens]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma lipophilum|M. lipophilum]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma lucivorax|M. lucivorax]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma luminosum|M. luminosum]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma maculosum|M. maculosum]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma melaleucae|M. melaleucae]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma meleagridis|M. meleagridis]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma microti|M. microti]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma moatsii|M. moatsii]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma mobile|M. mobile]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma molare|M. molare]]'' *''[[Mycoplasma muscosicanis|M. muscosicanis]]'' *'